then it became national news.

00:39:03.580 --> 00:39:08.070
And Rachel Maddow, and CNN,
everyone was talking about it.

00:39:08.070 --> 00:39:10.342
But that was one of
those situations where

00:39:10.342 --> 00:39:11.550
you don't realize the impact.

00:39:11.550 --> 00:39:12.300
You never know.

00:39:12.300 --> 00:39:13.925
You just basically
go in there, and let

00:39:13.925 --> 00:39:15.780
people-- Stephen Colbert, again.

00:39:15.780 --> 00:39:18.030
I go back to Stephen Colbert,
because he said to me

00:39:18.030 --> 00:39:19.650
when I first
started at the show.

00:39:19.650 --> 00:39:21.880
He said, when you put a
camera in someone's face,

00:39:21.880 --> 00:39:23.350
