00:39:23.350 --> 00:39:26.250
And you want to take advantage
of that as much as you can.

00:39:26.250 --> 00:39:28.680
And the other thing
is, use the silence.

00:39:28.680 --> 00:39:33.230
When you don't speak, they
will continue to speak,

00:39:33.230 --> 00:39:35.350
and they will fill the silence.

00:39:35.350 --> 00:39:39.500
And eventually, they will
do the thing which I call,

00:39:39.500 --> 00:39:42.430
I fucked the chicken moment.

00:39:42.430 --> 00:39:45.486
They will say, I
fucked the chicken.

00:39:45.486 --> 00:39:48.710
And once they say, I fucked the
chicken, you have your piece.

00:39:48.710 --> 00:39:49.880
That's it.

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:51.270
Then you can just be like--
