00:39:51.270 --> 00:39:51.786
We're good here.

00:39:51.786 --> 00:39:52.776
Oh, we've got everything.

00:39:52.776 --> 00:39:54.234
You pretty much
fucked the chicken?

00:39:54.234 --> 00:39:55.370
Yeah, I fucked the chicken.

00:39:55.370 --> 00:39:58.120
So sometimes it
takes a long time

00:39:58.120 --> 00:39:59.870
to get to the I fucked
the chicken moment.

00:39:59.870 --> 00:40:03.470
And sometimes, they say, I
fucked the chicken right away.

00:40:03.470 --> 00:40:05.870
But eventually, hopefully,
if the piece goes well, they

00:40:05.870 --> 00:40:07.472
