00:40:42.970 --> 00:40:46.594
And so once he
went on that roll,

00:40:46.594 --> 00:40:48.510
I knew that I just had
to stay out of the way.

00:40:48.510 --> 00:40:52.240
Now, my job was not to
encourage or discourage.

00:40:52.240 --> 00:40:54.814
It was just to step
back and let him go.

00:40:54.814 --> 00:40:56.980
And that's what happened,
