It's like a daycamp.

00:48:35.390 --> 00:48:36.847
It's like a retreat.

00:48:36.847 --> 00:48:38.680
AUDIENCE: It's like a
playground for adults.

00:48:38.680 --> 00:48:39.721
AASIF MANDVI: It is, yes.

00:48:39.721 --> 00:48:44.093
I have not seen one
person coding, nowhere.

00:48:45.958 --> 00:48:48.208
MALE SPEAKER: Yeah, you told
him to shut his computer.

00:48:51.312 --> 00:48:53.520
AASIF MANDVI: Of course,
