00:48:57.725 --> 00:48:58.600
You were on Facebook.

00:49:01.200 --> 00:49:05.548
You were tweeting, I'm sitting
in [INAUDIBLE] right now.

00:49:05.548 --> 00:49:06.970
No.

00:49:06.970 --> 00:49:08.080
But what did you say?

00:49:08.080 --> 00:49:09.720
Has it changed my opinion?

00:49:09.720 --> 00:49:12.690
Not one iota, no.

00:49:12.690 --> 00:49:13.620
It was a movie.

00:49:13.620 --> 00:49:17.350
And so obviously, there
were wild inaccuracies

00:49:17.350 --> 00:49:20.550
