00:49:25.630 --> 00:49:27.400
They were like,
now, we will again,

00:49:27.400 --> 00:49:30.560
have our next screening
of, "The Internship."

00:49:30.560 --> 00:49:34.210
You will get an F for the
semester if you don't watch it.

00:49:34.210 --> 00:49:38.190
AUDIENCE: So you had said
that when you came to the UK,

00:49:38.190 --> 00:49:42.730
