00:51:14.720 --> 00:51:17.200
Yes, absolutely.

00:51:17.200 --> 00:51:20.550
But I think,
hopefully, now what I

00:51:20.550 --> 00:51:25.460
do is, I just show them
my "Daily Show" card

00:51:25.460 --> 00:51:27.110
and get right through security.

00:51:29.860 --> 00:51:31.489
Yes, right here.

00:51:31.489 --> 00:51:32.030
AUDIENCE: Hi.

