So I'm also a child
of immigrants.

00:51:34.671 --> 00:51:35.670
AASIF MANDVI: Yes, good.

00:51:35.670 --> 00:51:36.230
Good.

00:51:36.230 --> 00:51:37.670
AUDIENCE: Trinidadian
immigrants.

00:51:37.670 --> 00:51:39.480
So West Indian, not East Indian.

00:51:39.480 --> 00:51:41.500
AASIF MANDVI: Well, "The Mystic
Masseur" was set in Trinidad.

00:51:41.500 --> 00:51:42.250
AUDIENCE: Yeah, Naipaul.

00:51:42.250 --> 00:51:43.150
AASIF MANDVI: And I
