00:51:43.150 --> 00:51:44.067
accent for that movie.

00:51:44.067 --> 00:51:44.816
AUDIENCE: Did you?

00:51:44.816 --> 00:51:46.460
AASIF MANDVI: Do you
do a Trini accent?

