AUDIENCE: See, don't
put me on the spot.

00:51:47.340 --> 00:51:48.000
AASIF MANDVI: Come on.

00:51:48.000 --> 00:51:49.000
AUDIENCE: I can't do it.

00:51:49.000 --> 00:51:50.920
AASIF MANDVI: I'll do
